common_issues.title: native_extensions_plugin.dll crash in Pieces OS 11.3.3
common_issues.description: Pieces OS 11.3.3 crashes on Windows due to native_extensions_plugin.dll.  Reinstalling, disabling antivirus/firewall, and updating graphics drivers do not resolve the issue.  A user also reported a conflict with the Pieces plugin in Visual Studio 2022 where the Diagnostic Tools pane is blank when the plugin is enabled. Disabling the plugin restores the pane's functionality.  A solution to disable the plugin is requested.
